*Pita* se da li će se sve ovo promeniti. (It is asked if all this will change.)

Ona je *pitala* zašto je to uradio. (She asked why he did that.)

Oni su *pitali* da li imam iskustva u oblasti. (They were asking if I have any experience in the field.)

Ona *pita* sebi da li je to dobro za nju. (She is asking herself if it is good for her.)

Oni su se *pitali* da li će ih poslušati. (They were wondering if they will be listened to.)